text: Tom O'Connell (born 14 June 2000) is an Australian cricketer who plays as a bowling all-rounder, bowling right-arm leg spin. He made his List A debut for Victoria in the 2018–19 JLT One-Day Cup on 16 September 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for the Melbourne Stars in the 2018–19 Big Bash League season on 14 January 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Australian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Melbourne Stars cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers
